    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"224323\">Junyan Xu</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/217875-Is-there-code-for-X.3F/topic/Finiteness.20of.20residue.20fields.20for.20number.20fields/near/516049323\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>it's implicit in the definition of <code>Ring.DimensionLEOne</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Oops. Why are there duplicate APIs (<code>Ring.KrullDimLE</code>)?</p>",
